{"tid":1914440,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[高達]你地翻工遇過最麻煩既人事/問題係點?(集思廣益)","createTime":"2020-03-07T13:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T05:47:35.000Z","uid":343020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"639f6ccb1c2c264357d67e50eceb1a0b5de91963","tid":1914440,"uid":343020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T13:48:42.000Z","msg":"大家好,又係我高達,以下係我既新片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>同同事唔夾?做得唔開心?你可能忽略的三個職場處理技巧|我溝YouTube觀眾/老闆/同事的策略</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0v80RFvVJTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0v80RFvVJTc&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=317e2eaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0v80RFvVJTc</a><br />\n<br />\n你地翻工遇過最麻煩既同事/問題係點? 大家可以集思廣益,係呢到互相share經驗,睇下會唔會對各位以後搵食處事有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見過一個最搞笑的案例係成間細公司都係親戚黎,當你家丁妹仔,靠熟人入行轉工，全世界都是這樣，不是壞事。用人唯親，那些親人，有些是廢人，這是管理的另一問題。 so, 前後者要分開看待及處理。太pk 的公司，越早離開，未必是唔好的。冇謂死磨。<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n自問唔係專家，只係一些透過個人經驗不斷學習翻黎的心得和分享<br />\n我既目標係希望盡量幫香港人可以搜集一些實用/含經濟效益/搵到食既資料<br />\n<br />\n計劃黎緊主要會上載既片/資源題材包括<br />\n求職/轉工<br />\n職業發展<br />\n進修〔搵下有冇啲可以幫大家有一技之長/移民(唔係冇選擇都唔鼓勵)加分既知識〕<br />\n其他實用野等等...稔到再整<br />\n<br />\n大家如果係搵工／進修上面有咩疑難都可以盡量係到問，我答到盡力答,多謝<br />\n<br />\n也可以在<strong>Google form</strong> 內問,分享,我會儲埋一齊在頻道制作一條QnA回答<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScJyap0xTFD2Tbv07Y91hyTI84P5fvYcMuHwMRpewfRppMh9Q/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScJyap0xTFD2Tbv07Y91hyTI84P5fvYcMuHwMRpewfRppMh9Q%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=8d8d8f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScJyap0xTFD2Tbv07Y91hyTI84P5fvYcMuHwMRpewfRppMh9Q/viewform?usp=pp_url</a><br />\n<br />\n其他有用資訊<br />\n<strong>轉工攻略:包裝自己可以sell既技能有咩?</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O2_GcY9H6ZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO2_GcY9H6ZA&d=z2r7XlCbtqTRl1EuzFzNuMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=4512f349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O2_GcY9H6ZA</a>"},{"pid":"5f18fab0fe62de0a295c8678dfe456b467f7f2a6","tid":1914440,"uid":249475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030ad19186520099f356ee7a0ef1bff3bf9da03e","tid":1914440,"uid":249475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd2003b3938336fcaa8483c21b014edef214877","tid":1914440,"uid":249475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65e15d8d26931cb06e2c282e46690d8f7ddb73b","tid":1914440,"uid":249475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}